      <div type="apparatus">
        <head>Apparatus</head>
		<div n="39">
		<p>ii. l. 1,  <foreign lang="grc"><supplied reason="lost">Νυμφάων τ</supplied>έμενος</foreign> cj. Feissel</p>
        <p>ii. l. 2,  The initial <foreign lang="grc">Α</foreign> in <foreign lang="grc">Ἀφροδισίαδος</foreign> is written <foreign lang="grc">Λ</foreign>. and the remaining traces of the first <foreign lang="grc">Ο</foreign> look more like an <foreign lang="grc">Α</foreign>.</p>
        <p>ii. l. 3,  <foreign lang="grc"><supplied reason="lost">φεισάμενος</supplied></foreign> conjectured by Merkelbach</p>
        <p>ii. l. 4,  <foreign lang="grc"><supplied reason="lost">ἀίδ</supplied><unclear reason="damage">ι</unclear>ον</foreign> conjectured by Merkelbach</p>
		</div>
